def transform_dataset(input_list):
    output_list = []
    current_id = None
    current_group = []
    
    for item in input_list:
        if item[0] != current_id:
            if current_group:
                # Extend each sublist to contain 11 elements
                while len(current_group) < 11:
                    current_group.append('')
                output_list.append(current_group)
            # Start a new group
            current_id = item[0]
            current_group = item[:]
        else:
            current_group.extend(item[1:])
    
    # Handle the last group
    if current_group:
        while len(current_group) < 11:
            current_group.append('')
        output_list.append(current_group)

    return output_list

output_list = transform_dataset(input_list)
print(output_list)
